window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>From the co-host of </i><b><i>Awareness Explorers</i></b><i> podcast comes a fresh approach to meditation and self-help, focusing on play instead of on work or effort.</i></p> <p><i>Awareness Games</i> teaches ways to play with your mind to point it toward the infinite well of happiness and joy that is within. Play with pure awareness, and discover the background of all experience, where happiness is hiding in plain sight. Create more joy. Uncover the secret of happiness. Play <i>Awareness Games</i>.&nbsp;</p>"; 
